>\n政府都鳩婚 東華都要高調解話調查<br />\n依班so call 有心人仲係到撐 <br />\n如果係真心 咁佢地個腦應該裝屎<br />\n會唔會係有班老師玩曲線咋"},{"pid":"598bf2c08ef6410b4a12cb4755be60b69b0aa74b","tid":1061620,"uid":32588,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:57:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而根據發起聯署人公布的名單，截止下午參與聯署的 92 人，只有 50 人是具名聯署，當中教師只有 7 人，校長和副校長則有36人</span><br />\n連名都唔敢出就唔好學人聯署啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但邊個用真名就立即起佢底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如搞個組織叫「愛護校長力量」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614313914a21d71c36b478230c88eadeec256ab4","tid":1061620,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"拿，公平d<br />\n<br />\n你校長果邊搵條友出黎跳樓死<br />\n<br />\n我咪信你囉"},{"pid":"bb4478b127b4984716056e15b540f1af73662be3","tid":1061620,"uid":3068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:23:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「一群無政治立場，只談教育的教育界僕人」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77affe9d85085ac4cdb38bdd28a8e45e7cde397","tid":1061620,"uid":180302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:25:44.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 啲仆街校長 屌老師就得<br />\n然後社會評論下你地<br />\n就聯署叫人唔好評論 校本身好大壓力<br />\n係唔係痴撚線 真係以為自己惡曬<br />\n你高高在上屌人就得 人屌你就妖魔化你<br />\n風頭火勢仲搞啲咁既野 真係以為自己大曬<br />\n唔接受批評 只可以我批評人"},{"pid":"1a964870e79ca013f23e2ef4028106d7a04e627a","tid":1061620,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:29:36.000Z","msg":"條八婆本身就係妖魔，何來妖魔化？"},{"pid":"87d537bd2b6ead84362514a1b5a9e85fa43467cf","tid":1061620,"uid":19501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:38:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聯署支持解僱羅婉儀人數